# Build artifacts
# NEW0 deliverable: track reproducibility surface, ignore scratch.
# See docs/active_plans/new0_outside_review_handoff.md.
# Note on rule shape: a directory ignored with `experiments/` cannot have its
# children re-included via negation. The form below ignores contents of each
# subdir with `dir/*`, then negates the specific files we keep, so git still
# recurses into the path.
tests/fixtures/
experiments/*
!experiments/css_native_layout/
experiments/css_native_layout/*
!experiments/css_native_layout/README.md
!experiments/css_native_layout/PRECHECK_SUMMARY.md
!experiments/css_native_layout/PRECHECK_USAGE.md
!experiments/css_native_layout/DECISION_MEMO.md
!experiments/css_native_layout/LAYOUT_SCORECARD.md
